Write a program that calculate sum of numbers
 1 to 100 in c++
Here is one possible solution in C++:

```c++
#include <iostream>
using namespace std;

int main() {
  // initialize variables
  int sum = 0;
  int i = 1;

  // loop through numbers 1 to 100
  while (i <= 100) {
    // add current number to sum
    sum += i;
    // increment counter variable
    i++;
  }

  // print the final sum
  cout << "The sum of numbers 1 to 100 is: " << sum << endl;

  return 0;
}
```

This program is similar to the Python version

, but uses the `cout` statement to print out the final sum. The output should be:

```
